Mozambuild is the leading and most well established, construction, building and interiors trade event in Mozambique. Organised since 2012, the 4th edition of Mozambuild will take place from 15 17 March 2017, at the Joaquim Chissano International Conference Centre, Maputo, Mozambique.Previous editions attracted over 80 exhibitors from 15 countries. The event will feature a three day trade exhibition, a series of technical and corporate workshops and a specially targeted B2B meetings. All of the aforementioned will be enhanced by a targeted visitor promotion campaign, aimed at maximising the amount of qualified industry visitors attending the event.The growth rate of the Mozambican economy is expected to increase from 2017, after ending 2016 with the lowest value in the last 15 years, of just 3.6%.However, with an average rate of 4.4% in 2017/2018 and 5.3% in 2019/2021, growth of Mozambique s economy will still be far from the average of 7.3% that was achieved in the period between 2005 and 2015.For further information about the event, please visit the official website www.mozambuild.comFor media accreditation, please contact:Alexia Claire, Marketing Assistant, AME Trade Ltd, Tel: +44 207 700 4949Email: &#x6d;&#x61;&#x72;&#107;&#101;tin&#x67;&#x40;&#x61;&#x6d;&#101;tra&#x64;&#x65;&#x2e;&#x6f;&#114;g